{"tid":1903903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今年九月立法會選舉得返兩派","createTime":"2020-02-29T09:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T09:19:22.000Z","uid":28914,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad06800a8893da3cf7ec75b169e1b15411647c2","tid":1903903,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T09:10:42.000Z","msg":"就係攬炒同非攬炒派<br />\n乜嘢「重奪議會」「關鍵一席」「議會抗爭」<br />\n根本就無可能發生<br />\n<br />\n一嚟民主黨、專業議政班友根本無可能同你玩癱瘓議會<br />\n二嚟冗長嘅議員工作只會消耗我地嘅精力，你睇吓班區議員就知道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只有<br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將議會變成攬炒一部分</span></span>」<br />\n先係出路<br />\n而第一步就係！<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">任何非攬炒派嘅人都唔應該進入立法會</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持攬炒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係非攬炒派"},{"pid":"5eb93db5ca8fbb54f6f5bbd607bbfe7274e6cc9f","tid":1903903,"uid":28914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T09:11:49.000Z","msg":"我就攬炒派嘅"},{"pid":"5d369dc351b9d67fc246fb2ddd61cca4dd3e1aa7","tid":1903903,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T09:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd9ad7176049e23f35365dd4e565afa191b9d6a","tid":1903903,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T09:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ec58a17b41232bbff986a2a30937b76612e4ad","tid":1903903,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62cc804b52887d68bca94cb1bcf90993380e181","tid":1903903,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike"